#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:3
msgid "Tidelift"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:5
msgid ""
"pytest is a member of `Tidelift`_. This document describes how the core team "
"manages Tidelift-related activities."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:9
msgid "What is it"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:11
msgid ""
"Tidelift aims to make Open Source sustainable by offering subscriptions to "
"companies which rely on Open Source packages. This subscription allows it to "
"pay maintainers of those Open Source packages to aid sustainability of the "
"work."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:16
msgid "Funds"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:18
msgid ""
"It was decided in the `mailing list`_ that the Tidelift contribution will be "
"split evenly between members of the `contributors team`_ interested in "
"receiving funding."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:21
msgid "The current list of contributors receiving funding are:"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:23
msgid "`@asottile`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:24
msgid "`@blueyed`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:25
msgid "`@nicoddemus`_"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:27
msgid ""
"Contributors interested in receiving a part of the funds just need to submit "
"a PR adding their name to the list. Contributors that want to stop receiving "
"the funds should also submit a PR in the same way."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:31
msgid ""
"The PR should mention `@pytest-dev/tidelift-admins`_ so appropriate changes "
"can be made in the Tidelift platform."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:34
msgid ""
"After the PR has been accepted and merged, the contributor should register "
"in the `Tidelift`_ platform and follow the instructions there, including "
"signing an `agreement`_."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:38
msgid "Admins"
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:40
msgid ""
"A few people have admin access to the Tidelift dashboard to make changes. "
"Those people are part of the `@pytest-dev/tidelift-admins`_ team."
msgstr ""

#: ../../../TIDELIFT.rst:43
msgid ""
"`Core contributors`_ interested in helping out with Tidelift maintenance are "
"welcome! We don't expect much work here other than the occasional adding/"
"removal of a contributor from receiving funds. Just drop a line to one of "
"the `@pytest-dev/tidelift-admins`_ or use the mailing list."
msgstr ""
